<br>
I can't say that never chaining will result in a bad outcome.  There are plenty of respectable magicians that do not chain cast pets.<br>
<br>
On the other hand, if you never master chaining, it will tend to leave you with more and more downtime as you progress past level 50.  That is, if you solo.  If you group, chaining is generally a non-issue unless things go wrong.<br>
<br>
